robertianburns.cryptarchsarchive

Class DataAccessObject_LoreEntrySelectionDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • robertianburns.cryptarchsarchive.ManifestDefinition
      • robertianburns.cryptarchsarchive.DataAccessObject_LoreEntrySelectionDefinition

  • public class DataAccessObject_LoreEntrySelectionDefinition
extends ManifestDefinition
    The Data access object type for record (what I call Lore Entry Selection) definition.

    This is used to access DestinyRecordDefinition from Destiny 2's manifest (destiny2_manifest in assets > databases). The manifest is a collection compressed SQLite files holding static definitions of objects found within Destiny.

    1.0.0
